Hello, I am taking over a project to integrate some data into HubSpot. So far so good, but I am getting to the final step which is to edit some contacts and want to create associations.

I want to do this in bulk using `<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/contact/batch/update>`

Is it possible to update the contacts object and create associations in a single API call?

This is the data I am sending to test, but only the properties are getting updates.

```{
  "inputs": [
    {
       "id": "123123123",
        "properties": {
            "prop1": "823828232",
            "pro2": true
        },
        "associations": [
            {
            "to": {
                "id": "098098890"
            },
            "types": [
                {
                "associationCategory": "USER_DEFINED",
                "associationTypeId": 78
                }
            ]
            }
        ]
    }
  ]```
